[Name] Bogofilter
[Summary] A mail filter that classifies mail as spam or ham (non-spam)
[Description] Bogofilter is a mail filter that classifies mail as spam or ham (non-spam) by a statistical analysis of the message's header and content (body). The program is able to learn from the user's classifications and corrections.
